# Domain Types Rules

`lib/types/index.ts` is the **single source of truth** for:

- `UserRole`, `BookingStatus`, `MemberTier`, `VehicleSize`, `BookingType`
- API request/response interfaces
- UI maps: `BOOKING_STATUS_CONFIG`, `TIER_LABELS`, `VEHICLE_SIZE_LABELS`

## When Adding Types

- Align names with BE Swagger field names where possible
- Add Vietnamese labels to UI helper maps in the same file
- Do not duplicate enums in `lib/data.ts`

## Booking Status

Always use full API status keys (`PENDING_CONFIRMATION`, not `PENDING`). `StatusBadge` has legacy mapping for old mock keys only.

## Business Constants

| Concept | Values |
|---|---|
| Booking type | `WASH` (lift bay) vs `FLEX` (no lift) |
| Trust score | 100 start; <60 no pay-after-service; <20 no booking |
| Tier window | MEMBER 3d, SILVER 7d, GOLD 10d, PLATINUM 14d |
